# Communication Plan

## Purpose
To ensure timely and effective communication among all project stakeholders.

## Stakeholders & Communication Methods
| Stakeholder           | Communication Type   | Frequency      | Responsible |
|-----------------------|-------------------|---------------|------------|
| Project Sponsor        | Email / Meeting   | Weekly         | Project Manager |
| Development Team       | Stand-up Meetings | Daily          | Project Manager |
| QA Team                | Reports           | Twice a week   | QA Lead       |
| End Users              | Updates           | Monthly        | Product Manager |
| Steering Committee     | Reports / Meeting | Bi-weekly      | Project Manager |

## Tools
- Email  
- MS Teams / Zoom  
- Google Docs / Sheets  

## Notes
- Meeting minutes will be recorded and shared.  
- All project changes communicated through formal channels.
